{"tid":898945,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"自由可以絕無節制嗎？","createTime":"2018-11-12T05:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T09:11:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc81b77cd50460592526521147da04e794346ac9","tid":898945,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/古德明/daily/article/20181112/20543645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F20543645&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=f628bade\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F20543645&h=72dbec2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/古德明/daily/article/20181112/20543645</a><br />\n<br />\n自由可以絕無節制嗎？ - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20181112/large/e8811a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20181112%2Flarge%2Fe8811a.jpg&h=ad45a699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n鄭月娥政府驅逐英國記者馬凱，敲響了香港言論自由的喪鐘，天下皆聞。上月十九日，日本放送協會記者以此問鄭月娥；本月六日，聯合國人權理事會也以此問張建宗，張、鄭的答案都是：「天下沒有絕無節制的自由。」這句話，香港小民應會越來越常聽見。<br />\n<br />\n天下萬事，當然都不能絕無節制。人不可以不食，但飲食無節制將癡肥；不可不眠，但睡眠無節制將損健康。然則統治者奪饑民口中糧，濫刑者令囚犯連日不得睡覺，一定也可以說：「飲食與睡眠，天下那有絕無節制者？」這樣的中共式國際標準，香港高官現在已經運用自如了。<br />\n<br />\n其實自由要節制，就應先節制有權力者。在舊中國，君主雖然獨裁，也不能不受傳統禮教、百官諫諍等節制，小事如行幸遊獵，大事如刑法之施，往往都受掣肘，不得自由，以至宋神宗曾發脾氣說：「快意事更做不得一件！」還給大臣教訓說：「如此快意，不做得也好！」（《蓼花洲閑錄》）今天，民主國家更有國會、法庭、選舉等等制度，節制統治者權力。<br />\n<br />\n中共只會說「天下沒有絕無節制的自由」，但統治者的自由卻要絕無節制。於是他們實行「三權合作」，以及「我有權擇官，你無權選擇」式普選。於是鄭月娥有自由以小民膏血填滄海，習近平更有自由以小民膏血遍灑他邦。至於小民，當然不能說沒有反對自由，只是自由不可「絕無節制」而已。  <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n日本人與酒 (高慧然)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n「活化」 (尊子)"},{"pid":"a83053b6776e31ac830a301b86cfcb78b46fea9c","tid":898945,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"自由行可以絕無節制嗎？"},{"pid":"54b18f9b2f40caedb8bbb16928e205dfc6712d9e","tid":898945,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a83053b6776e31ac830a301b86cfcb78b46fea9c","tid":898945,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"自由行可以絕無節制嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181110/large/10la4p13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181110%2Flarge%2F10la4p13.jpg&h=65d2acfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181110/large/10la4p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181110%2Flarge%2F10la4p11.jpg&h=27f7ab83&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}